item.title: Red Team Recon Writeups
item.author: James S
item.description: This is a writeup for the room Red Team Recon on tryhackme here Built-in Tools When was thmredteam.com created (registered)? (YYYY-MM-DD) 2021-09-24, got from whois. To how many IPv4 addresses does clinic.thmredteam.com resolve? 2, got from dig. To how many IPv6 addresses does clinic.thmredteam.com resolve? 2, got from dig with -6 flag. Advanced Searching How would you search using Google for xls indexed for http://clinic.thmredteam.com? filetype:xls site:clinic.thmredteam.com How would you search using Google for files with the word passwords for http://clinic.
